*******
module
  emitMessage
    type
*******

mCore Emitter
  toEngine
    state: change some parameter
    send:   build message
  fromEngine
    client: send message to client instance
    log: status messages
  fromCore
    data:   output to transport (buffer)
  toCore
    data:   parse from transport (buffer)

mEngine Emitter
  toEngine
    state: intercept self, and pass to parent if appropriate
    send:   intercept self, pass to parent
  fromEngine
    client: intercept, parse, and pass to self emitter
    log: status messages
  (LINKED TO PARENT mCore or mEngine EMITTER)

mSession emitter
  fromClient
    xport:  set some property
    send: build a message
    session: set some property in session
  toClient
    config: full config pull
    log: data out
    client: parsed message data

mTransport emitter
  fromTransport
    connect
    disconnect
    data

  toTransport

  (LINKED TO DEVICE EMITTER)
